---
title: Orkney Crab and King Prawn Mac and Cheese with Baby Leaf and Tomato Salad
description: A comfort food classic using premium ingredients, this Orkney Crab and King Prawn Mac and Cheese brings the best of the British pub into your kitchen.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R33_W34_UK_SS24013-7_Main_low-a632212f.jpg
